You are analyzing code for **Command Injection (OS Command Injection)** vulnerabilities.

## What Is Command Injection?

Command injection occurs when an application passes user-controlled input to a system shell command without proper sanitization. An attacker can append or inject shell metacharacters (`;`, `|`, `&&`, `$(...)`, backticks) to execute arbitrary operating system commands on the server, potentially gaining full system access.

